snippet.title: Ultimate Fishing Simulator - Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Ultimate Fishing Simulator is a realistic fishing game, made using the latest computer technology. The game has the most advanced water system in the world, offers photo-realistic graphics, complex fish AI and much more!

Whether you are a fisherman or not - it doesn’t matter! This game is for everyone!

Choose your fishing technique and try your luck fishing in different parts of the world. From the tiny roaches to the huge marlins!

Support us on Kickstarter:
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1752350052/ultimate-fishing-simulator

Steam:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/468920/Ultimate_Fishing_Simulator/

Facebook:
https://www.facebook.com/UltimateGamesCom

Spread the word about the game!
